com.serena.dmclient.api
Class TransferCommandDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.TransferCommandDetails
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeliverCommandDetails, DownloadCommandDetails, UploadCommandDetails
public class TransferCommandDetails
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to specify the generic command details for the Project Upload and Download methods. . Boolean flags are set/retrieved as Boolean objects. It is intended that the absence of a flag will result in the corresponding parmeter not being passed to the underlying command. The default will be used by the command. Setting an explict Boolean will cause this to be passed to the underlying command.
